| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3906 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonransomware)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e36beec7-7c07-52af-9486-8c71ec98a3e2"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
